**Common Cybersecurity Reports**
1 Incident Report - Details a cyber attack or breach 
2 Vulnerability Assessment Report - Lists security weaknesses found in systems 
3 Penetration Testing Report - Shows how systems were hacked during testing 
4 Risk Assessment Report - Identifies risks and their impact on business 
5 Compliance / Audit Report - Checks if company follows standards like NIST, ISO 
6 Threat Intelligence Report - Information about current cyber threats 
7 Security Monitoring / SOC Report - Daily/weekly logs and alerts from security operations 


